        <qualifiedname>bt_conn_le_cs_subevent_result::frequency_compensation</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Frequency compensation value in units of 0.01 ppm. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This is a 15-bit signed integer in the range [-100, 100] ppm.</para>
<para>A value of <ref refid="hci__types_8h_1a385a401b373522160b1832b66838e02d" kindref="member">BT_HCI_LE_CS_SUBEVENT_RESULT_FREQ_COMPENSATION_NOT_AVAILABLE</ref> indicates that the role is not the initiator, or that the frequency compensation value is unavailable. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
